    "en": {
      "title": "All five days of the school week in the south: three days a week in other provinces",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education states that government and government approved schools will resume from tomorrow.",
        "The Ministry of Education also says that from now on every week on Monday, Tuesday and Thursday, schools will be opened on time and on Wednesdays and Fridays, students will be taught online.",
        "Meanwhile, the Southern Provincial Council says that the schools governed by the Southern Provincial Council will be opened on all five days of the week."
      ],
